dc_title_s: Roads Fond du Lac County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Roads_2014.gdb. [The roads layer depicts road centerlines for roads in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download
